{"tid":2162324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★電視廣播(00511.HK)與優酷簽戰略合作協議","createTime":"2020-08-18T05:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:02:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"63bae73d702c20556241a700a143947c6bd5b649","tid":2162324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"電視廣播(<a href=\"http://00511.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00511.HK&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=b9270a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00511.HK</a>)  公布，日前與內地三大視頻平台之一優酷簽訂戰略合作協議，將在影視、綜藝、藝人、電子商貿、串流媒體平台等五大方向全力發展，進一步在內地建立具廣泛影響力的「新港味泛粵娛樂」產業和市場陣地。<br />\n<br />\n在影視領域方面，將進一步開拓版權開發與發行、劇集及綜藝合拍、合製的空間。藝人方面，公司的豐富經驗將和內地行業資源和市場更加深入互動，大大提升其商業價值。另外，公司的內容IP和藝人資源會更進一步和優酷平台資源結合，在電商直播等新業務方面謀求新的突破和發展<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.1036129/latest-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2FNOW.1036129%2Flatest-news&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF%2F%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=425e6c93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.1036129/latest-news</a>"},{"pid":"88afd01928a9cd1bb94077e3edf67ad19f85837f","tid":2162324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8efa06752ea8dda9ed2988478453c39cf49f2852","tid":2162324,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T05:19:10.